[[image:Beppu-station.jpg|250px|thumb|Beppu Station]]
{{nihongo|'''Beppu Station'''|<U+5225><U+5E9C><U+99C5>|Beppu-eki}} is the main [[railway station]] for the city of [[Beppu]] in [[<U+014C>ita Prefecture]], [[Japan]], which is famous for its [[onsen]]. It is situated on the [[Nipp<U+014D> Main Line]]. The station, and all trains serving it, are operated by [[JR Ky<U+016B>sh<U+016B>]].

==Limited Express Trains==
* [[Sonic (train)|Sonic]] ([[Hakata Station|Hakata]] - [[<U+014C>ita Station|<U+014C>ita]])
* [[Nichirin]] (Hakata - [[Miyazaki Station|Miyazaki]])
* [[Yufuin-no-mori|Yufuin-no-mori, Yufu]] (Hakata - Beppu)
* [[Trans-Kyushu Limited Express]] (Beppu - [[Hitoyoshi Station|Hitoyoshi]])

==Layout==
There is two [[side platform]]s and four [[island platform]]s. 

